      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "However, this card is shockingly takeable act 1, when you may actually want to switch to and ignite the inferno early. Most obvious versus gremlin nob, where playing this turn 2 deals 12 Soulburn + 12 damage, plus you'll be back on the first Searing Ghostflame on the following turn which means 6 more Soulburn.",
